Speaker 2: Oh, good morning! Yes, it is. The sun is shining, the birds are chirping. It's just a perfect day.

Speaker 2: It's doing fairly well. I'm expecting a good harvest of tomatoes soon. And how's your dog, Sparky?

Speaker 1: Ah, the unsung heroes of the office world. We teachers also appreciate a well-stocked break room.

Speaker 2: I bet you do. Well, I better head off. Those coffee pots won't fill themselves.

Speaker 1: Ha, that's true. Have a great day!

Speaker 2: You too! Say hi to Sparky for me.

Speaker 1: Will do. Enjoy your day at the office!

Speaker 2: Thanks, I will. Take care!
